Revision history for Test-CPAN-Health

0.01
  - Initial release on CPAN.
  - 22 health checks covering packaging, quality, security, and CI categories.
  - Four report formats: terminal (ANSI colour), JSON, HTML, and TAP.
  - CLI script cpan-health with --format, --min-score, --skip, --check,
    --no-network, --no-cover, --output, and --cache-dir options.
  - SQLite result cache (~/.cache/cpan-health/) for expensive checks.
  - Hard caps: SecurityAdvisories fail caps score at 60; CPANTesters fail
    caps score at 75.
